- STACEY sworn. - Q. What are you? - A.I am servant to Mr. John Dobree, Charing-cross, who is a pawnbroker; this pair of stockings was pledged on the 22d of June, between seven and eight o'clock in the morning, by one of the women;
Charlotte Glover
, and the prisoners came in, but I cannot say which pledged them for nine-pence.
